soot.jimple.spark.geom.heapinsE

Class HeapInsNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.jimple.spark.geom.geomPA.IVarAbstraction
      • soot.jimple.spark.geom.heapinsE.HeapInsNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Numberable

    public class HeapInsNode
extends IVarAbstraction
    This class defines a pointer variable for use in the HeapIns encoding based points-to solver. HeapIns is a simpler form of geometric encoding. HeapIns is faster and uses less memory, but also, it is less precise than geometric encoding. NOT recommended to use.
